quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  55,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  55,1,rehman ne
  55,2,iss quran ki taleem di hai
  55,3,usi ne ensaan ko peda kya
  55,4,aur usay bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Sooraj aur chaand aik hisaab ke paband hain
  55,6,aur tarre aur darakht sab sajda raiz hain
  55,7,aasman ko uss ne buland kya aur maizaan qaim kar di
  55,8,iss ka taqaza yeh hai ke tum maizaan mein khlal nah daalo
  55,9,insaaf ke sath theek theek tolo aur traazo mein dandi nah maro
  55,10,zameen ko is ne sab makhloqaat ke liye banaya
  55,11,is mein har terhan ke bakasrat lazeez phal hain khajoor ke darakht hain jin ke phal ghlafon mein liptay hue hain
  55,12,terhan terhan ke ghallay hain jin mein bhosa bhi hota hai aur dana bhi
  55,13,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki kin kin nematon ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,14,ensaan ko uss ne theekri jaisay sokhey srhe hue gaaray se banaya
  55,15,aur jin ko aag ki lapat se peda kya
  55,16,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ke kin kin ajaaeb qudrat ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,17,"dono mashriq aur dono maghrib, sab ka maalik o parvar-digaar wohi hai"
  55,18,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,19,do samndron ko is ne chore diya ke baahum mil jayen
  55,20,phir bhi unn ke darmain aik parda haail hai jis se woh tajawaz nahi karte
  55,21,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki qudrat ke kin kin karishmo ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,22,inn samndron se moti aur mongay nikaltay hain
  55,23,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki qudrat ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,24,aur yeh jahaaz usi ke hain jo samandar mein pahoron ki terhan ounchay utthay hue hain
  55,25,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ke kin kin ahsanat ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,26,har cheez jo is zameen par hai fanaa ho jaane wali hai
  55,27,aur sirf tairay rab ki jallel o kareem zaat hi baqi rehne wali hai
  55,28,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ke kin kin kamalaat ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,29,zameen aur asmano mein jo bhi hain sab apni hajtein usi se maang rahay hain har aan woh nai shaan mein hai
  55,30,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki kin kin sifaat Hamida ko jhutlao ge ?"
  55,31,"ae zameen ke bojho, anqareeb hum tum se baz purse karne ke liye farigh hue jatay hain"
  55,32,( phir dekh len ge ke ) tum apne rab ke kin kin ahsanat ko jutlatay ho
  55,33,"ae giroh jin o ans, gir tum zameen aur asmano ki sarhadoon se nikal kar bhaag satke ho to bhaag dekho nahi bhaag satke iss ke liye bara zor chahiye"
  55,34,apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,35,( bhagnay ki koshish karo ge to ) tum par aag ka shola aur dhuwan chore diya jaye ga jis ka tum muqaabla nah kar sakuu ge
  55,36,"ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ka inkaar karo ge ?"
  55,37,phir ( kya banay gi uss waqt ) jab aasman phatay ga aur laal chamray ki terhan surkh ho jaye ga ?
  55,38,ae jin o ans ( uss waqt ) tum apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,39,uss roz kisi ensaan aur kisi jin se uss ka gunah poochnay ki zaroorat nah hogi
  55,40,phir ( dekh liya jaye ga ke ) tum dono giroh apne rab ke kin kin ahsanat ka inkaar karte ho
  55,41,mujrim wahan apne cheharon se pehchan liye jayen ge aur inhen peshani ke baal aur paon pakar pakar kar ghsita jaye ga
  55,42,uss waqt tum apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,43,( uss waqt kaha jaye ga ) yeh wohi jahannum hai jis ko mujrimeen jhoot qarar diya karte thay
  55,44,usi jahannum aur kholtey hue pani ke darmain woh gardish karte rahen ge
  55,45,phir apne rab ki kin kin qudraton ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,46,"aur har uss shakhs ke liye jo apne rab ke huzoor paish honay ka khauf rakhta ho, do baagh hain"
  55,47,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,48,hari bhari daaliyon se bharpoor
  55,49,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,50,dono baghoon mein do chashmay rawan
  55,51,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,52,dono baghoon mein har phal ki do kasmain
  55,53,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,54,"janati log aisay farshon par takiye laga ke bathain ge jin ke Aster dabeez resham ke hon ge, aur baghoon ki dalian phalon se jhuki par rahi hon gi"
  55,55,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,56,inn nematon ke darmain Sharmeeli nigahon waleyan hon gi jinhein inn jannatiyon se pehlay kisi ensaan ya jin ne chuva nah hoga
  55,57,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,58,aisi khobsorat jaisay heere aur moti
  55,59,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,60,neki ka badla neki ke siwa aur kya ho sakta hai
  55,61,"phir ae jin o ans, apne rab ke kin kin Awsaf Hamida ka tum inkaar karo ge ?"
  55,62,aur unn do baghoon ke ilawa do baagh aur hon ge
  55,63,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,64,ghany sirsabz o shadaab baagh
  55,65,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,66,dono baghoon mein do chashmay fawaron ki terhan ubaltay hue
  55,67,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,68,unn mein bakasrat phal aur khjorin aur aanar
  55,69,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,70,inn nematon ke darmain khoob seerat aur khobsorat biwiyan
  55,71,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,72,khaimon meintehrai hui hooren
  55,73,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,74,inn jannatiyon se pehlay kabhi ensaan ya jin ne unn ko nah chuva hoga
  55,75,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,76,woh janati sabz qalinon aur nafees o nadir farshon par takiye laga ke bathain ge
  55,77,apne rab ke kin kin inamaat ko tum jhutlao ge ?
  55,78,barri barket wala hai tairay rab jallel o kareem ka naam
